data.description: Well maintained home in the Cloverleaf Estates. Located on a large corner lot with a fully fenced backyard with two separate gates. This home is a gardener's dream with beautiful garden beds, plants and roses. Also, an underground sprinkler system for the front and backyard. Plenty of storage with sheds and a nice deck off of the Primary suite. Newer roof and water heater. All appliances are included. Indoor washer and dryer, pantry, and a garage door opener. Enjoy the abundance of natural light with the vaulted ceilings and skylights. Display your knick-knacks on the decorative lofts. Three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The primary suite boasts two separate bathing areas. One with a large garden tub. This house is clean and move in ready !
